        </div>

      </article>

    </section>

    <section class="productSection">
      <div class="prod-sect-img-wrap img-left" style="background:url('{{theme.link}}/images/products/duet/004_firstKind.jpg') no-repeat top center; background-size:cover;">
        <img class="left phone-only" src="{{theme.link}}/images/products/duet/004_firstKind.jpg">
      </div>
      <div class="productText">
        <h2>First of Its Kind</h2>
        <p>
          The first-ever multitouch table with independent and switchable Windows 8 and Android systems has finally arrived. Its large, bright screen comes with industry-leading touch technology from 3M™. The Duet redefines computing for the home and public spaces.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="productSection plain phone-only platform-coffee full bleeder">
      <img class="right phone-only" src="{{theme.link}}/images/products/duet/005_doubleDown.jpg">
      <div class="productText white fullLeft">
        <h2>Double Down</h2>
        <p> 
          Why limit yourself to one system, when you can run two? With two independent computer systems, you have the flexibility you need for performance and productivity. This  dual-boot system provides ample power to run just about any PC or Android application. 
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="productSection plain tablet-n-desktop platform-coffee full bleeder" style="background-image:url('{{theme.link}}/images/products/duet/005_doubleDown.jpg');">
      <div class="productText white fullLeft">
        <h2>Double Down</h2>
        <p> 
          <!-- Why limit yourself to one system, when you can run two?  With two independent computer systems, millions of PC and Android apps are at your fingertips. Custom software provides a seamless switch between operating systems. A powerful Intel Core and Rockchip system provide ample power to run just about any PC or Android application. -->
          Why limit yourself to one system, when you can run two? With two independent computer systems, you have the flexibility you need for performance and productivity. This  dual-boot system provides ample power to run just about any PC or Android application.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    
    <section class="section-info">
      <h1>Key Features</h1>
    </section>

    <ul
      class="slider platform-coffee"
      ng-init="clientSliderIndex = 0"
      rn-carousel
      rn-carousel-control
      rn-carousel-indicator
      rn-carousel-width="responsiveTwoUp()"
      rn-carousel-index="clientSliderIndex"
    >
      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder twotimes">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/timestwo.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Times Two</h3>
        <p>
          The Duet includes an Intel® Quad Core i5 3.20GHZ with 8GB RAM or i7 3.5GHz with 
          16GB RAM and Windows 8.1 Professional and an Android Rockchip RK3288 2.0 GHz system.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder edison">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/edison.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Intel Edison</h3>
        <p>
          At the core of the Duet coffee table is Intel’s Edison, a small, powerful mini-computer, 
          which has been programmed to facilitate the seamless switch between the Android and Windows 
          8 systems.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/reach.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Reach Out &amp; Touch Everything</h3>
        <p>
          Along with an industry-leading, up-to-60 touch points<sup>*</sup> for the touch surface, 
          the Duet Coffee Table has a bright HD resolution screen, and up to a 60hz refresh 
          rate. (<sup>*</sup>Android OS caps points at 12)
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/demanding.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Built for Demanding Spaces</h3>
        <p>
          The Duet multitouch coffee tables have a chemically strengthened glass top and 
          the chassis is made out of aircraft-grade aluminum and cold-rolled steel. It 
          is perfect for public spaces and other demanding environments. The table can 
          travel too. It can fit through standard doorways even when packed in a protective 
          ATA case (upgrade option).
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/gestureworks.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Creation by Intelligent Design</h3>
        <p>
          The Duet comes with a lifetime license for GestureWorks Core and Open Exhibits. 
          The license includes ticketed, timely support (one year is included free*) and 
          free upgrades for life. GestureWorks Gameplay is also included.
        </p>
      </li>

      <li class="client-slide" ng-class="{active: clientSliderIndex==0}">
        <div class="svgHolder">
          {% include '/images/products/svg/warranty.svg' %}
        </div>
        <h3>Two Year Warranty</h3>
        <p>
          We stand by our products and provide a two-year warranty. The same people who build our products, provide support. See our 
          <a href="http://ideum.com/spec-sheets/Ideum-2year-Touch-Product-Warranty.pdf" target="_blank">warranty document</a> 
          for full details and restrictions.
        </p>
      </li>

    </ul>

    <a class="very-dark-gray-button" href="http://ideum.com/spec-sheets/Ideum-Specs-Duet.pdf">Download Spec Sheet</a>

    <section class="productSection plain platform-coffee full" 
    style="background:url('{{theme.link}}/images/products/duet/006_hubConnect.jpg') no-repeat top center; background-size:cover;">
      <div class="productText white fullRight">
        <h2>The Hub of the Connected Home</h2>
        <p>
          The Duet coffee table can be a hub in home and public spaces, allowing you to control devices and environment -- all from one centralized location. It’s the command center you’d envisioned for the future, made possible today by the innovative design and technology of Ideum. 
