        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="productSection">
      <div class="prod-sect-img-wrap img-right" 
      style="position:relative !Important;background:url('{{theme.link}}/images/products/duet/007_bestBuilt.jpg') no-repeat center center; background-size:cover;">
        <img class="right" src="{{theme.link}}/images/products/duet/007_bestBuilt.jpg" style="visibility:hidden;">
      </div>
      <div class="productText">
        <h2>The Best Built Touch Tables. Period.</h2>
        <p>
          Sleek and slim, the Duet multitouch coffee table is also just as tough and secure as all the other tables that have helped to make Ideum so well-known around the globe, since 2008. Ideum stands behind their products, and offers prompt, reliable service — to ensure that this smart multitouch coffee table will continue to meet your needs for museums, schools, store-settings, lobbies, or home.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="productSection plain platform-coffee full" 
    style="background:url('{{theme.link}}/images/products/duet/008_3MTouch.jpg') no-repeat top center; background-size:cover;">

      <div class="productText white fullLeft">
        <h2>3M Touch is Better</h2>
        <p> 
          The Duet has a sleek, bezel-less design, and uses an industry leading 3M touch controller.
          <div class="specs">
            <ul class="specList">
              <li>Bezel-free design</li>
              <li>Fast &lt;12 multitouch response time</li>
              <li>60 touch points (Android capped at 12)</li>
            </ul>

            <ul class="specList column2">
              <li>Anti-glare coating</li>
              <li>Chemically strengthened glass</li>
              <li>1080p ultra-thin HD LCD display</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="made-in-usa platform-coffee">

      <h2>
        Made in the USA
      </h2>

    </section>

    <section class="productSection">
      <div class="prod-sect-img-wrap img-left" style="background:url('{{theme.link}}/images/products/duet/009_directSales.jpg') no-repeat top center; background-size:cover;">
        <img class="left phone-only" src="{{theme.link}}/images/products/duet/009_directSales.jpg">
      </div>
      <div class="productText">
        <h2>Direct Sales &amp; Rentals</h2>
        <p>
          Please contact us at <span class="faux-link">(505) 792-1110</span> ext. 1 or toll free in the US and Canada <span class="faux-link">(855) 898-6824</span>, use our online inquiry form, or email us at <a href="&#109;&#97;&#105;&#108;&#116;&#111;&#58;&#115;&#97;&#108;&#101;&#115;&#64;&#105;&#100;&#101;&#117;&#109;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;">&#115;&#97;&#108;&#101;&#115;&#64;&#105;&#100;&#101;&#117;&#109;&#46;&#99;&#111;&#109;</a>. Ideum's 46" Multitouch Coffee Table is sold domestically and internationally, direct from Ideum. We also rent the 42” and 46” multitouch coffee tables in the US and Canada.
        </p>
        <p class="note">Please note - the 42" is not available for sale internationally.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

</main>
{% endblock %}
